# .trivyignore — fixable-but-unfixed CVEs as of helm 3.20.2 release (2026-04-09).
#
# These are HIGH/CRITICAL CVEs that Trivy reports as fixable, but where the
# Helm upstream binary has not yet shipped the patched dependency. Re-evaluate
# on every Helm bump; remove the entry as soon as Helm ships with the fix.
#
# Audit cadence: every PR that bumps HELM_VERSION must rerun the Trivy scan
# locally and prune entries here.
# Last audited: 2026-05-11 (against helm 3.20.2).

# ── grpc CVE-2026-33186 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# google.golang.org/grpc v1.72.2 → fixed in 1.79.3.
# Helm 3.20.2 still ships grpc 1.72.2; CVE pending in helm 3.20.3 / 3.21.0.
CVE-2026-33186

